Sentencas: Novel cathode materials for solid oxide fuel cells based on Ba-doped Sr2Fe1.5Mo0.5O6 (Sr2-x Ba-x Fe1.5Mo0.5O6-delta where x = 0.3, 0.5, 0.7 and 0.9) were synthesized by solution combustion method and sintered at 1200 degrees
Titulo: Novel cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells based on Ba-doped Sr2Fe1.5Mo0.5O6

Sentencas: C. Their phase composition, microstructure and electrical conductivity were studied.
Titulo: Novel cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells based on Ba-doped Sr2Fe1.5Mo0.5O6

Sentencas: It was shown that the maximal electrical conductivity of 18.5 S/cm at 450 degrees C was measured for the Sr1.3Ba0.7Fe1.5 Mo0.5O6-delta ceramics.
Titulo: Novel cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells based on Ba-doped Sr2Fe1.5Mo0.5O6

Sentencas: The superior chemical compatibility between the Sr2-x Ba-x Fe1.5Mo0.5O6-delta cathode and Gd0.2Ce0.8 O-1.9 electrolyte was confirmed, as well as good matching between thermal expansion coefficients of the cathode and electrolyte materials.
Titulo: Novel cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells based on Ba-doped Sr2Fe1.5Mo0.5O6
